# ngx_http_heavybag_module - scanner / security-tool User-Agent signatures
#
# $waf_type = scanner. With `waf_bot_block on` these are dropped (404),
# matching the module's original hardcoded behaviour. One case-insensitive
# PCRE2 fragment per line; '#' comments and blank lines ignored. Tokens are
# matched unanchored against the raw User-Agent header (use ^ to anchor).
#
# Hot-reloadable: `nginx -s reload` re-reads and recompiles this file.

sqlmap
nikto
nmap
masscan
zgrab
nuclei
dirbuster
gobuster
wpscan
acunetix
nessus
netsparker
fimap
hydra
arachni
dirsearch
openvas

